casebody.data:
Lawrence JOHNSON, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-9894. Supreme Court of the United States May 27, 2014. Case below, 551 Fed.Appx. 22 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied. Justice SOTOMAYOR took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
